<TBLCELL ROWSEP="HSINGLE" COLSTART="1">
<FONT font-name="SymbolMT" font-size="10.98pt">•</FONT>
<FONT font-name="Calibri" font-size="10.98pt">The OTIP program has been around 6 full years as of December 31, 2019 (the date of the above statistical
reporting);</FONT>
</TBLCELL>
</TBLROW>
</TBLROWS>
</TBLHEAD>
<TBLBODY TBLWD="600">
