<TBLCELL ROWSEP="HSINGLE" COLSTART="1">
<FONT font-name="SymbolMT" font-size="10.98pt">•</FONT>
<FONT font-name="Calibri" font-size="10.98pt">Using basic averages, that means that the OTIP program has received on average 917 phone calls per year;</FONT>
</TBLCELL>
</TBLROW>
<TBLROW>
<TBLCELL ROWSEP="HSINGLE" COLSTART="1">
<FONT font-name="SymbolMT" font-size="10.98pt">•</FONT>
<FONT font-name="Calibri" font-size="10.98pt">The program has received on average 267 potential informants per year;</FONT>
</TBLCELL>
</TBLROW>
<TBLROW>
<TBLCELL ROWSEP="HSINGLE" COLSTART="1">
<FONT font-name="SymbolMT" font-size="10.98pt">•</FONT>
