</TBLROW>
<TBLROW>
<TBLCELL ROWSEP="HSINGLE" COLSTART="1">
<FONT font-name="SymbolMT" font-size="10.98pt">•</FONT>
<FONT font-name="Calibri" font-size="10.98pt">The amount of reassessed tax dollars has been $10 million per year with only $3.33 million collected on average
per year;</FONT>
</TBLCELL>
</TBLROW>
</TBLROWS>
</TBLBODY>
